room_title: Escape room "Deception Depot" by Big Sky Breakout in Missoula
room_description: It's the wild west here Kid Curry and his gang are fixin’ to hold up a train. Curry’s lost his touch for the outlaw life, and you ain’t havin’ it. Your splinter gang is going to double cross Kid Curry and grab the loot before it even leaves the station. It won’t bother you none if Kid Curry takes the fall. You’ll be countin’ your money while he’s wailing his way to county jail!
